snippet: There is currently no evidence that NASCAR champion driver Tony Stewart committed a crime when he struck and killed a fellow driver in a weekend race, the Sheriff of Ontario County, New York, said on Monday....

headline.print_headline: No Charges for Now Against NASCAR's Stewart in Fatal Crash: Sheriff
headline.main: No Charges for Now Against NASCAR's Stewart in Fatal Crash: Sheriff

lead_paragraph: There is currently no evidence that NASCAR champion driver Tony Stewart committed a crime when he struck and killed a fellow driver in a weekend race, the Sheriff of Ontario County, New York, said on Monday.
